msgid "Eymet, bastide vivante du Périgord"
msgstr "Eymet, a Living Bastide in the Périgord"

msgid "Le Margo, au cœur de la place, entre arcades médiévales et douce vie périgourdine."
msgstr "Le Margo, in the heart of the square, between medieval arcades and the sweet Périgord lifestyle."

msgid "Contact : "
msgstr "Contact: "

msgid "Bastide de 1270"
msgstr "Bastide since 1270"

msgid "Plan en damier, arcades, halle… une balade historique à deux pas du restaurant."
msgstr "Checkerboard layout, arcades, market hall… a historical stroll just steps from the restaurant."

